Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這些也壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能買新的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了還能用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是非得新的才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?還是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去好好上課嗎?學分都拿到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為籐本君總是只顧著打工...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩又摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼走在平地上也會摔倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝

